{"tid":1367101,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"求求求 黑白game","createTime":"2019-07-26T07:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T18:58:25.000Z","uid":61473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fe366795bec3f1496aee814f3194139d53068059","tid":1367101,"uid":61473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:04:35.000Z","msg":"求求求game<br />\n記得以前玩過兩款黑白遊戲<br />\n<br />\n一隻是2D射擊<br />\n用電腦玩的, 黑白2D射擊, 背景白底, 人物黑色<br />\n每次開始前有武器可以選, 每橫走100m 可以幫人物升lv/補血<br />\n狙擊槍過1000m 可以變激光<br />\n<br />\n第二款是手機遊戲<br />\n2d non-stop run, 黑白遊戲<br />\n人物只會向前跑, 但玩家就要用操作令背景平整, 令人物可以順利前行<br />\n令背景平整包括: 令高低地面整平, 斬樹枝, 打石頭etc"},{"pid":"f1b7b203a942773f9154640e95fcbffa30778a5d","tid":1367101,"uid":61473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:04:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ff0a5d4990c6ff85572d2b82bec36a681bc287d","tid":1367101,"uid":61473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:29:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c3decf2c3a082fc7272d45204d108ab6e9e19ed","tid":1367101,"uid":61473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:17:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22f3c7fecaa25bdb7ec58b7fc4ce7a63ec40bc11","tid":1367101,"uid":61473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:58:25.000Z","msg":"推"}]}